  "name": "Gross Profit Report - Invoiced",
  "body": "<h1 data-id=\"gross-profit-report-invoiced\">Gross Profit Report - Invoiced</h1>\n<p>Use the Gross Profit Report - Invoiced to view details of Awaiting Payment and Processed invoices within the selected period, including Invoiced COGS, Sales $ and GP.</p>\n<ul><li>A maximum date range of one month can be applied</li><li>The report works purely on invoiced goods and does not take into consideration Fulfilled or Unfulfilled status</li></ul><p>To use the Gross Profit Report - Invoiced:</p>\n<ol><li>Navigate to<strong> Reports &gt; Sales Report &gt; Gross Profit Report - Invoiced</strong></li><li>Update the <strong>Filters </strong>as required<br/><img alt=\"User-added image\" height=\"482\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41215PM.05T5g000018qHP2EAM.jpg\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 482px; width: 900px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41215PM.05T5g000018qHP2EAM.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41215PM.05T5g000018qHP2EAM.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41215PM.05T5g000018qHP2EAM.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41215PM.05T5g000018qHP2EAM.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41215PM.05T5g000018qHP2EAM.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41215PM.05T5g000018qHP2EAM.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at41215PM.05T5g000018qHP2EAM.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Click <strong>Search</strong></li><li>The results will be displayed<br/><img alt=\"User-added image\" height=\"482\" src=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at42643PM.05T5g000018qHSzEAM.jpg\" width=\"900\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"height: 482px; width: 900px\" srcset=\"https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=300,width=300/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at42643PM.05T5g000018qHSzEAM.jpg 300w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=600,width=600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at42643PM.05T5g000018qHSzEAM.jpg 600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=800,width=800/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at42643PM.05T5g000018qHSzEAM.jpg 800w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1200,width=1200/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at42643PM.05T5g000018qHSzEAM.jpg 1200w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=1600,width=1600/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at42643PM.05T5g000018qHSzEAM.jpg 1600w, https://us.v-cdn.net/cdn-cgi/image/quality=80,format=auto,fit=scale-down,height=2000,width=2000/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at42643PM.05T5g000018qHSzEAM.jpg 2000w, https://us.v-cdn.net/6038474/uploads/attachments/migrated/Screenshot20240131at42643PM.05T5g000018qHSzEAM.jpg\" sizes=\"100vw\" class=\"embedImage-img importedEmbed-img\"></img></li><li>Click the <strong>disk icon </strong>in the toolbar to select from a range of export options</li></ol><p>View this report in-page, print or Export to Excel.</p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"#Top\">Return to Top</a></p>",
